The,service,provides,records,of,plant,anatomy,structure,and,phenotype,It,aims,to,compile,validated,profiles,of,agricultural,crops,including,inter,relationships,visible,traits,and,measurements,It,defines,concepts,for,defining,agronomic,databases,and,the,records,they,contain,Accurate,descriptions,and,mapping,of,agronomic,phenotypes,supports,comparative,research,into,phenotypes,and,genotypes,and,experiments,in,gene,discovery,API,methods,support,both,keyword,search,across,the,database,and,more,focused,retrieval,of,ontologies,defined,by,the,service,and,their,component,categories,Methods,provide,access,to,root,terms,within,an,ontology,and,parent,child,structural,relationships,among,terms,Methods,also,support,creating,new,ontologies,within,the,database,and,deletion,of,existing,ones